
<h1>Gimmie'dat'Burger!</h1>
<div class="add">  
<h2>Add a burger</h2>

<form id="create-form"> 
  <div class="form-group">
    {{!-- <label for="ca">burger Name:</label> --}}
    <input type="text" id="ca" name="name">
    <button type="submit">Add burger</button>
  </div>
</form>
<p style="color:red;">Think of Gimmie'dat'Burger as a burger bucket list. Add burgers you would love to devour some day. Once you've 
  enjoyed a burger simply click the devoured button to add it to the devoured list. Accidentally click devoured? simply
  click the Undevour button to add that burger back to the other side.
</p>
</div> 

<div class="flexbox-container">
<div class="flexbox-item flexbox-item-1">
<h1>Burgers that I have not devoured Yet!</h1>

<ul>
  {{#each burgers}}
  {{#unless devoured}}
  {{> burgers/burger-block devoured=false}}
  {{/unless}}
  {{/each}}
</ul>
</div>

<div class="flexbox-item flexbox-item-2">
<h1>Burgers that I have devoured!</h1>

<ul>
  {{#each burgers}}
  {{#if devoured}}
  {{> burgers/burger-block devoured=true}}
  {{/if}}
  {{/each}}
</ul>
</div>

</div>